<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF346A8BF81E90C5162DBCCB" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF346A8BF81E90C5162DBCCB" blockId="207.[2017,2612,1582,2001]" lastBlockId="207.[1403,2613,2008,3463]" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">
Subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF78490C516CABD8F" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[2168,2250,1692,1725]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF71E90C51759BD8F" baseAuthorityName="Temminck" baseAuthorityYear="1840" box="[2274,2393,1692,1725]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="horsfieldii">horsfieldii</taxonomicName>
species group. See 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF7E0909116B7BDD7" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1824" box="[2076,2231,1736,1765]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="adversus">M. adversus</taxonomicName>
. There are at least two species of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF7BB90B21699BC3E" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[2119,2201,1771,1804]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
in New 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF346A8BF6E890B2177ABC3E" box="[2324,2426,1771,1804]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">Guinea</collectingCountry>
: 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF67190B21434BC3E" baseAuthorityName="Gould" baseAuthorityYear="1854" box="[2445,2612,1771,1804]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macropus">M. macropus</taxonomicName>
and specimens currently attributed to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF81E916316AEBC69" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[2018,2222,1850,1883]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="moluccarum">M. moluccarum</taxonomicName>
that could represent a distinct species. Sampling from across the distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF74891D0177DBC98" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1915" box="[2228,2429,1929,1962]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="moluccarum">M. moluccarum</taxonomicName>
is needed to fully understand its taxonomy and how it relates to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF9FF918118A7BCCB" baseAuthorityName="Gould" baseAuthorityYear="1854" box="[1539,1703,2008,2041]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macropus">M. macropus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF346A8BF91791811984BCCB" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1824" box="[1771,1924,2008,2041]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="207" pageNumber="970" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="adversus">M. adversus</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF346A8BFA809E5D1771B3A5" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FF346A8BFA809E5D1771B3A5" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398954" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398954" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398954/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="207" pageNumber="969" targetBox="[1402,1994,1588,2003]" targetPageId="207">
