), Kai Is, New 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF346A8BF7199E76174BB37A" box="[2277,2379,2095,2120]" name="Guinea-Bissau" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">Guinea</collectingCountry>
including Raja Ampat Is (Waigeo, Batanta), Karkar I, 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF346A8BF84C9E1716EBB35D" box="[1968,2283,2126,2159]" name="Papua New Guinea" pageId="207" pageNumber="969">Bismarck Archipelago</collectingCountry>
